    "segments": [
      {
        "start_time": "0:01",
        "end_time": "0:02",
        "text": "What?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:02",
        "end_time": "0:02",
        "text": "No!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:03",
        "end_time": "0:04",
        "text": "Yes way!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:04",
        "end_time": "0:05",
        "text": "It's time for..."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:05",
        "end_time": "0:06",
        "text": "News for Kids!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:07",
        "end_time": "0:08",
        "text": "News for Kids!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:08",
        "end_time": "0:09",
        "text": "真的假的!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:10",
        "end_time": "0:12",
        "text": "原來是..."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:13",
        "end_time": "0:16",
        "text": "不止你不知道的趣味新鮮室"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:16",
        "end_time": "0:18",
        "text": "ICRNT's News for Kids!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:29",
        "end_time": "0:32",
        "text": "How much sugar is in your drinks?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:32",
        "end_time": "0:34",
        "text": "You might be surprised!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:35",
        "end_time": "0:37",
        "text": "你知道裡面有多少糖嗎?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:37",
        "end_time": "0:39",
        "text": "很驚人喔!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:39",
        "end_time": "0:43",
        "text": "Having too many sugary drinks isn't good for you."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:44",
        "end_time": "0:50",
        "text": "In Taiwan, it's a top cause for kidney problems for young people."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:50",
        "end_time": "0:55",
        "text": "And more young people are having kidney problems than before."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:56",
        "end_time": "1:06",
        "text": "喝太多含糖飲料對身體不好,糖分也是引發台灣年輕人腎臟病的頭號原因。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:06",
        "end_time": "1:10",
        "text": "而且,越来越多年轻人有这个问题,"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:24",
        "end_time": "1:28",
        "text": "这是因为台湾到处都买得到含糖饮料,"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:29",
        "end_time": "1:34",
        "text": "每走几步,就会看到一间手摇饮或是茶水店。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:46",
        "end_time": "1:57",
        "text": "喝飲料時最好點無糖的,但如果你真的很想喝含糖飲料,醫生建議一星期最多喝三次。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:07",
        "end_time": "2:15",
        "text": "Your body doesn't need to break down drinks, so sugar goes into your blood fast."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:16",
        "end_time": "2:17",
        "text": "That's not good for you."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:18",
        "end_time": "2:28",
        "text": "含糖飲料比甜點更糟糕,因為甜點被消化時,糖分會慢慢的滲透進血液。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:28",
        "end_time": "2:37",
        "text": "但飲料不需要被身體分解,所以糖分會快速跑進血液裡,這樣很不健康。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:37",
        "end_time": "2:39",
        "text": "Forget sugary drinks."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:40",
        "end_time": "2:42",
        "text": "Water is the best drink."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:44",
        "end_time": "2:45",
        "text": "Vocabulary"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:45",
        "end_time": "2:49",
        "text": "口渴的时候,喝水最好也最健康。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:49",
        "end_time": "2:50",
        "text": "Sugar"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:51",
        "end_time": "2:51",
        "text": "糖"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:51",
        "end_time": "2:52",
        "text": "What would you like to drink?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:53",
        "end_time": "2:53",
        "text": "Coffee?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:53",
        "end_time": "2:54",
        "text": "Tea?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:54",
        "end_time": "2:55",
        "text": "你想喝什么?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:55",
        "end_time": "2:56",
        "text": "咖啡还是茶?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:57",
        "end_time": "2:58",
        "text": "I like to have Coke."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:58",
        "end_time": "3:00",
        "text": "我想喝可乐。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:00",
        "end_time": "3:02",
        "text": "Coke has too much sugar."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:02",
        "end_time": "3:04",
        "text": "可乐含有太多糖了。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:04",
        "end_time": "3:06",
        "text": "Worst 比较坏的。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:06",
        "end_time": "3:08",
        "text": "Maybe a sports drink?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:08",
        "end_time": "3:10",
        "text": "也許喝個運動飲料。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:10",
        "end_time": "3:12",
        "text": "Isn't that just as sugary?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:13",
        "end_time": "3:15",
        "text": "那不是跟可樂一樣多糖?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:15",
        "end_time": "3:19",
        "text": "No, coke is worse 不會,可樂更糟糕。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:20",
        "end_time": "3:21",
        "text": "How much 多少?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:22",
        "end_time": "3:24",
        "text": "How much sugar is in coke, do you know?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:25",
        "end_time": "3:27",
        "text": "可樂裡面有多少糖,你知道嗎?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:27",
        "end_time": "3:31",
        "text": "I don't, a lot I think, because it's sweet."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:31",
        "end_time": "3:34",
        "text": "不知道,我想有很多,因為它很甜。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:34",
        "end_time": "3:36",
        "text": "Hot 熱的"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:36",
        "end_time": "3:39",
        "text": "Are you sure you don't want some nice hot tea?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:39",
        "end_time": "3:42",
        "text": "你確定不想來點好喝的熱茶?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:42",
        "end_time": "3:45",
        "text": "No, thank you 不了 謝謝"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:45",
        "end_time": "3:47",
        "text": "Can I have my coke now?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:47",
        "end_time": "3:50",
        "text": "現在我可以喝可樂了嗎?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:50",
        "end_time": "3:52",
        "text": "Oh, alright 好吧"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:52",
        "end_time": "3:55",
        "text": "你喜歡哪一種飲料呢?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:55",
        "end_time": "3:56",
        "text": "Sugar"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:57",
        "end_time": "3:57",
        "text": "糖"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:59",
        "end_time": "4:01",
        "text": "比較壞的"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:01",
        "end_time": "4:02",
        "text": "How much"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:04",
        "end_time": "4:04",
        "text": "多少"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:04",
        "end_time": "4:05",
        "text": "Hot"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:05",
